PSXC-IMDB UPGRADING:
--------------------

NOTE: If you use a different GLROOT than /glftpd, you most
      likely need to change a couple of variables in the files
      you replace.
      Using the installer will help you with this, and it is
      encouraged to use it. It should be quite safe - backups
      are taken and all actions questioned.
NOTE: Where I say "replace" below here, you can also patch.

2.8  -> 2.9  - replace psxc.imdb.sh and psxc-imdb-find.sh.
2.7g -> 2.7i - replace psxc-imdb.sh
             - replace psxc-imdb-find.sh
2.7f -> 2.7g - replace psxc-imdb.sh
2.7e -> 2.7f - replace psxc-imdb.sh
2.7d -> 2.7e - replace psxc-imdb.sh
2.7c -> 2.7d - Nothing, unless you get warnings when running the script.
		If you do, you should replace psxc-imdb.sh,
		psxc-imdb-sanity.sh, psxc-symlink-maker.sh.
2.7b -> 2.7c - replace psxc-imdb-find.sh
2.7  -> 2.7b - replace psxc-imdb.sh
2.6  -> 2.7  - replace psxc-imdb.sh
             - replace psxc-imdb-bot.tcl
